Intellect Design Arena
The stock has risen 48% so far this fiscal year, from Rs 693 to Rs 1,027, with FIIs holding 27.83% as of June 2025.
ETMarkets.com
6/11
CarTrade Tech
This stock saw a 47% gain in FY26, increasing from Rs 1,643 to Rs 2,424. FIIs hold a significant 67.30% stake as of June 2025.
ANI
7/11
KEI Industries
The share price grew 43% in FY26, rising from Rs 2,891 to Rs 4,141. FII ownership is 26.59% as of the June 2025 quarter.
ETMarkets.com
