Title   : Oil ministry queries Vedanta on demerger plan, flags financial risk at NCLT
Source  : www.livemint.com
Published: 2025-09-17T14:27:06
Fetched : 2025-09-18T15:16:53.002196
URL     : https://www.livemint.com/companies/vedanta-demerger-plan-anil-agarwal-national-company-law-tribunal-financial-disclosure-11758108030180.html
